::Shadow Wing::

She flew upward and heard the explosion of the fourth missle but didn't look 
back to see how the Predacons ended up.  She flew back to the arc.  She 
landed and walked in.  She heard the systems alert going off saying Intuder. 
  She went to the bridge and saw two other bots there.
"Who is breaking into the ship?  Does the internal scanners let us know who 
it is?"
